The Alex Jones Show
Sunday, 27 February 2011


[sebaygo1]


The 2 hour Sunday show is typically a review of the past week's news and a look forward to the coming week's events.

The Infowars web site describes today's broadcast as follows.

On this encore Sunday edition of the Alex Jones Show, Alex talks with investment analyst, entrepreneur, and publisher of the Gloom Boom & Doom Report, Marc Faber. Alex also talks with Washington, D.C.-based investigative journalist, author and columnist Wayne Madsen and radio and television personality Mancow Muller.
